    n = len(nums)
    result = [1] / n
    prefix = 1
    for i in range(n):
        result[i] = prefix
        prefix *= nums[i]
    suffix = 1
    for i in range(n - 1, -1, -1):
        result[i] *= suffix
        suffix *= nums[i]
    return result
